│ // This file implements the SLP vectorizer. It detects consecutive stores/loads                                                                                                          │
│ // that can be grouped into vector-operations. It also combines consecutive                                                                                                              │
│                                                                                                                                                                                          │
│ // arithmetic operations.                                                                                                                                                                │
│ //                                                                                                                                                                                       │
│ // The SLP-vectorizer processes the code bottom-up, starting from the stores                                                                                                             │
│ // and traversing the instructions upwards. It builds a tree of instructions                                                                                                             │
│ // that represent a data-flow graph. The leaves of the graph are load                                                                                                                    │
│ // instructions and constants. The nodes of the graph are arithmetic                                                                                                                     │
│ // instructions.                                                                                                                                                                         │
│ //                                                                                                                                                                                       │
│ // The vectorizer traverses the data-flow graph and checks if the instructions                                                                                                           │
│ // that are part of the graph are consecutive memory locations or consecutive                                                                                                            │
│ // arithmetic instructions that can be combined into vector instructions.                                                                                                                │
│ //                                                                                                                                                                                       │
│ // The inner loop of the vectorizer builds a cost model of the vector-form of                                                                                                            │
│ // the graph. It traverses the bottom-up data-flow graph and estimates the cost                                                                                                          │
│ // of the graph in vector form. If the vector form is cheaper than the scalar                                                                                                            │
│ // form, the vectorizer replaces the scalar instructions with vector                                                                                                                     │
│ // instructions.                                                                                                                                                                         │
│ //                                                                                                                                                                                       │
│ // For a more detailed explanation of the algorithm see:                                                                                                                                 │
